# TODO: Translation updated at 2026-03-05 21:40

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:37
translate spanish shani_conversations_289a209a:

    # Z "I have to leave for now."
    Z "Tengo que irme por ahora."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:40
translate spanish shani_conversations_735aa9a2:

    # S "Okay!"
    S "¡Vale!"

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:47
translate spanish s_convi_1_4f52e312:

    # Z "About the elf..."
    Z "Sobre la elfa..."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:50
translate spanish s_convi_1_fdba35f2:

    # S "Oh right, what happened to her?"
    S "Oh, sí, ¿qué pasó con ella?"

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:51
translate spanish s_convi_1_f142b97e:

    # S "You stayed away a full day, and you left for the desert without much equipment."
    S "Estuviste fuera un día entero, y te fuiste al desierto sin mucho equipo."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:52
translate spanish s_convi_1_a5fc91fa:

    # S "Did you find out what she wanted from you?"
    S "¿Averiguaste lo que quería de ti?"

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:55
translate spanish s_convi_1_7bc64da3:

    # Z "Yes, I followed her to a place where other mutants have come together."
    Z "Sí, la he seguido hasta un lugar donde se han reunido con otros mutantes."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:58
translate spanish s_convi_1_dc781d89:

    # Z "You should have seen it!"
    Z "¡Deberías haberlo visto!"

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:59
translate spanish s_convi_1_dd63f351:

    # Z "It was like a place out of time."
    Z "Era como un lugar fuera del tiempo."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:62
translate spanish s_convi_1_d642b0fa:

    # S "What do you mean?"
    S "¿Qué quieres decir?"

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:65
translate spanish s_convi_1_07c70d85:

    # Z "It's a bunker unlike any place I've scoured in many years of explorations."
    Z "Es un búnker que no se parece a ningún lugar que haya explorado en muchos años de exploraciones."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:66
translate spanish s_convi_1_f88a3e10:

    # Z "Fully functional, as far as I can tell, run by some source of energy that I had no idea still existed."
    Z "Totalmente funcional, por lo que puedo ver, alimentado por alguna fuente de energía que ni siquiera sabía que aún existía."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:69
translate spanish s_convi_1_893f55cf:

    # S "I don't get it..."
    S "No lo entiendo..."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:72
translate spanish s_convi_1_30e7e982:

    # Z "This was technology from before the End of Days."
    Z "Esto era tecnología de antes del Fin de los Días."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:73
translate spanish s_convi_1_906c1a84:

    # Z "They weren't really fully in control of it and I'm not sure everything worked as it should, because frankly, nobody alive knows what half the machines I saw even are meant to do."
    Z "En realidad, no lo controlaban del todo y no estoy seguro de que todo funcionara como debería, porque, francamente, nadie vivo sabe lo que hacen la mitad de las máquinas que vi."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:74
translate spanish s_convi_1_0705c33c:

    # Z "But there were more working machines and examples of antique technology being used as everyday tools than I have ever seen in one single place."
    Z "Pero había más máquinas en funcionamiento y ejemplos de tecnología antigua que se utilizaban como herramientas cotidianas de lo que jamás había visto en un solo lugar."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:77
translate spanish s_convi_1_f40f2fa7:

    # S "Is that something you should report to the [Q]?"
    S "¿Es algo de lo que debes informar a [Q]?"

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:80
translate spanish s_convi_1_f79cca8f:

    # Z "No, for now I think it is best that she doesn't know about it. I want to find out more, before I decide what to do with this information."
    Z "No, por ahora creo que es mejor que no lo sepa. Quiero averiguar más antes de decidir qué hacer con esta información."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:83
translate spanish s_convi_1_9283f33d:

    # S "I trust you, [persistent.dad]. I'm sure you know what's best."
    S "Confío en ti, [persistent.dad]. Estoy segura de que sabrás qué es lo mejor."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:86
translate spanish s_convi_1_632fe158:

    # Z "I hope I do, [S]. For now, do not tell anyone what I have seen. Especially not [Q]."
    Z "Eso espero, [S]. Por ahora no le digas a nadie lo que he visto. Y menos aún a [Q]."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:89
translate spanish s_convi_1_1e04ec68:

    # S "I won't. But what about the girl?"
    S "No lo haré. ¿Pero qué pasa con la chica?"

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:92
translate spanish s_convi_1_f2138ebd:

    # Z "They call her Ivy, and she's a mystery alright; to them too, apparently."
    Z "La llaman Ivy, y es un misterio; para ellos también, al parecer."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:95
translate spanish s_convi_1_c619e966:

    # S "Them, you mean the other mutants? What are they like?"
    S "¿Ellos? ¿Te refieres a los otros mutantes? ¿Cómo son?"

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:98
translate spanish s_convi_1_3e5f99f1:

    # Z "Yes, they too know little about her."
    Z "Sí, ellos también saben poco de ella."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:99
translate spanish s_convi_1_a7947467:

    # Z "As for them... they're, interesting."
    Z "En cuanto a ellos... son interesantes."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:103
translate spanish s_convi_1_cb6e550c:

    # Z "Let's be honest, they have a reason for what they do."
    Z "Seamos sinceros, tienen una razón para lo que hacen."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:104
translate spanish s_convi_1_23efb421:

    # Z "Zeta enslaves their kind, the decayed have them for dinner..."
    Z "Zeta esclaviza a los de su especie y los Decaídos se los comen..."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:105
translate spanish s_convi_1_17aecfe9:

    # Z "It was only a matter of time before they banded together."
    Z "Sólo era cuestión de tiempo que se unieran."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:106
translate spanish s_convi_1_719cec91:

    # Z "Their leader is very fierce about her goals."
    Z "Su líder defiende sus objetivos con ferocidad."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:107
translate spanish s_convi_1_65ed8321:

    # Z "And she doesn't rule out violence."
    Z "Y no descarta la violencia."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:110
translate spanish s_convi_1_1157eb80:

    # Z "Maybe she can be convinced that Zeta can change..."
    Z "Tal vez se la pueda convencer de que Zeta puede cambiar..."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:113
translate spanish s_convi_1_54e1747e:

    # S "You think it can?"
    S "¿Crees que puede cambiar?"

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:114
translate spanish s_convi_1_6b899421:

    # S "Didn't Zeta always enslave mutants?"
    S "¿Acaso Zeta no ha esclavizado siempre a los mutantes?"

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:117
translate spanish s_convi_1_bf791c23:

    # Z "I am not a historian, but I can't imagine it was always like this."
    Z "No soy historiador, pero me cuesta creer que siempre haya sido así."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:118
translate spanish s_convi_1_e690e7bb:

    # Z "What I know is that if we ignore this problem, it might one day be at our doorstep."
    Z "Lo que sé es que si ignoramos este problema, un día podría estar a nuestras puertas."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:119
translate spanish s_convi_1_db27b81f:

    # Z "And then it will be too late."
    Z "Y entonces será demasiado tarde."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:123
translate spanish s_convi_1_b44b1992:

    # Z "They're a sexy bunch, I'll give them that."
    Z "Hay que reconocer que están bastante buenas."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:126
translate spanish s_convi_1_5106592f:

    # S "Ugh, [persistent.dad]. Why!?!"
    S "Uff, [persistent.dad]. ¿¡Por qué!?"

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:129
translate spanish s_convi_1_dce5d3a8:

    # Z "Come now, [S], you know me..."
    Z "Venga, [S], ya me conoces..."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:130
translate spanish s_convi_1_971a98df:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:131
translate spanish s_convi_1_7be68858:

    # Z "Don't be mad, princess, you know I care about my family above all."
    Z "No te enfades, princesa. Sabes que mi familia me importa más que nada."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:134
translate spanish s_convi_1_d77cf90f:

    # S "Nice try, [persistent.dad]."
    S "Buen intento, [persistent.dad]."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:139
translate spanish s_convi_1_0d467650:

    # Z "They're quite the extremists... I had a conversation with their leader."
    Z "Son bastante extremistas... Tuve una conversación con su líder."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:140
translate spanish s_convi_1_09d9fd08:

    # Z "And she basically threatened the safety of the House, should I tell the Queen about their location."
    Z "Y prácticamente amenazó con atacar la Casa si le contaba a la Reina dónde se encuentran."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:143
translate spanish s_convi_1_ffe54f35:

    # S "What do you mean? Do they even know where to find us?"
    S "¿Qué quieres decir? ¿Saben siquiera dónde encontrarnos?"

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:146
translate spanish s_convi_1_513b3c22:

    # Z "They do. You're forgetting I brought Ivy right into our basement."
    Z "Así es. Olvidas que traje a Ivy a nuestro sótano."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:149
translate spanish s_convi_1_c4200914:

    # S "Uff... lovely."
    S "Uff... estupendo."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:152
translate spanish s_convi_1_bbff13f5:

    # Z "To be fair, mutants don't have it easy, you know that."
    Z "Siendo justos, los mutantes no lo tienen fácil. Ya lo sabes."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:153
translate spanish s_convi_1_452986ba:

    # Z "Until Zeta stops enslaving them and treating them like they do now, they won't stop fighting for change."
    Z "Mientras Zeta siga esclavizándolos y tratándolos así, no dejarán de luchar para cambiar las cosas."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:154
translate spanish s_convi_1_45af1d5e:

    # Z "But the methods... I'm not sure what to make of them."
    Z "Pero los métodos... No sé qué pensar de ellos."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:157
translate spanish s_convi_1_6a2934b9:

    # S "Can violence change things, though? Zeta has the largest number of warriors under its banner."
    S "¿Puede la violencia cambiar las cosas? Zeta tiene el mayor número de guerreros bajo su bandera."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:160
translate spanish s_convi_1_22c817b1:

    # Z "I don't know yet. They have some high quality military armor for sure."
    Z "Aún no lo sé. Desde luego, cuentan con equipo militar de gran calidad."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:161
translate spanish s_convi_1_8e129d88:

    # Z "Their bunker might contain some surprises, or maybe the surprise is the mutants themselves."
    Z "Su búnker podría contener algunas sorpresas, o tal vez la sorpresa sean los propios mutantes."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:162
translate spanish s_convi_1_3461e593:

    # Z "Who knows, they might have powers beyond good hearing and eyes that change colour."
    Z "Quién sabe, quizá tengan habilidades que vayan más allá de un oído excepcional y unos ojos que cambian de color."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:165
translate spanish s_convi_1_12eb0af7:

    # S "Eyes that change colour? Are you serious?"
    S "¿Ojos que cambian de color? ¿Hablas en serio?"

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:168
translate spanish s_convi_1_5a78ec10:

    # Z "I thought you'd noticed. It's a thing Ivy does. I'm not sure if any other mutant can do the same though."
    Z "Pensé que te habías dado cuenta. Ivy puede hacerlo. Aunque no sé si algún otro mutante tiene esa capacidad."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:171
translate spanish s_convi_1_7c16a8de:

    # Z "Anyway, maybe they don't mean us specifically any harm, especially if I play along and have a chance to find out more... But it's something to be mindful of."
    Z "De todos modos, puede que no quieran hacernos ningún daño en concreto, sobre todo si sigo el juego y tengo la oportunidad de averiguar más... Pero es algo a tener en cuenta."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:176
translate spanish s_convi_2_c4554330:

    # Z "So... what happened at the Queen's palace?"
    Z "Entonces... ¿qué ha pasado en el palacio de la Reina?"

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:179
translate spanish s_convi_2_08f09abd:

    # S "It was... something else."
    S "Fue... toda una experiencia."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:182
translate spanish s_convi_2_49e49167:

    # Z "How do you mean?"
    Z "¿A qué te refieres?"

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:185
translate spanish s_convi_2_f6383439:

    # S "She received me in the thermae instead of the throne room..."
    S "Me recibió en las termas en vez de en la sala del trono..."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:188
translate spanish s_convi_2_af2587ec:

    # Z "They are impressive, aren't they?"
    Z "Son impresionantes, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:191
translate spanish s_convi_2_bb986455:

    # S "They are, very much so."
    S "Lo son, y mucho."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:192
translate spanish s_convi_2_bc719c4d:

    # S "We didn't stay long, however..."
    S "Aunque no nos quedamos mucho tiempo..."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:193
translate spanish s_convi_2_762a29b3:

    # S "I know you didn't see everything, but do you remember that boy who wanted to kidnap [A]?"
    S "Sé que no lo viste todo, pero ¿recuerdas a ese chico que quería secuestrar a [A]?"

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:196
translate spanish s_convi_2_ef6ea3c4:

    # Z "Of course. If it wasn't for the guards, he'd long be cut into pieces."
    Z "Claro. Si no fuera por los guardias, hace tiempo que lo habría hecho pedazos."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:199
translate spanish s_convi_2_971a98df:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:206
translate spanish s_convi_2_b0f95b13:

    # S "That's pretty much what happened..."
    S "Eso es más o menos lo que pasó..."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:213
translate spanish s_convi_2_3cf11edf:

    # Z "What do you mean?"
    Z "¿Qué quieres decir?"

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:216
translate spanish s_convi_2_d9aaf7aa:

    # S "[Q] prepared a private execution, setting him up and cutting him up with a knife."
    S "[Q] organizó una ejecución privada: lo inmovilizó y empezó a cortarlo con un cuchillo."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:219
translate spanish s_convi_2_d0fa7644:

    # S "She seemed to enjoy the moment very much..."
    S "Parecía disfrutar muchísimo del momento..."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:222
translate spanish s_convi_2_81ca4981:

    # Z "I have noticed that she seems to enjoy testing the boundaries of her power."
    Z "Me he dado cuenta de que parece disfrutar probando los límites de su poder."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:223
translate spanish s_convi_2_ee5a6ae5:

    # Z "I am starting to think she might be a bit too young and unrestrained for the important position she holds in Zeta."
    Z "Empiezo a pensar que quizá sea demasiado joven e impulsiva para un cargo tan importante en Zeta."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:226
translate spanish s_convi_2_a921dc76:

    # S "She said that her people need to know what happens to criminals like him to feel safe."
    S "Dijo que su pueblo necesita saber qué les ocurre a los criminales como él para sentirse a salvo."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:231
translate spanish s_convi_2_f93e5888:

    # S "But even if he threatened [A] like that..."
    S "Pero aunque haya amenazado a [A] de esa manera..."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:234
translate spanish s_convi_2_b1c810c9:

    # S "I love her, and I would always protect her."
    S "La quiero, y siempre la protegería."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:237
translate spanish s_convi_2_cfbab307:

    # S "But torturing him like she did..."
    S "Pero torturarle así..."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:238
translate spanish s_convi_2_256a7a0d:

    # S "That's not the right thing, you know?"
    S "Eso no está bien, ¿sabes?"

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:241
translate spanish s_convi_2_b12413c1:

    # Z "Our old Queen, the one who ruled before Merneith, would have agreed with you."
    Z "Nuestra antigua Reina, la que gobernaba antes de Merneith, habría estado de acuerdo contigo."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:245
translate spanish s_convi_2_4a0f471a:

    # S "But it's not just that."
    S "Pero no es sólo eso."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:246
translate spanish s_convi_2_f3936f08:

    # S "He did deserve it."
    S "Él se lo merecía."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:247
translate spanish s_convi_2_6dd43cac:

    # S "He almost killed my sister, for what? Fame? Wealth?"
    S "Casi mata a mi hermana, ¿para qué? ¿Por la fama? ¿Riqueza?"

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:248
translate spanish s_convi_2_61cfabb0:

    # S "He deserved everything she did to him."
    S "Se merecía todo lo que ella le hizo."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:252
translate spanish s_convi_2_8318c16f:

    # S "Anyways..."
    S "En fin..."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:253
translate spanish s_convi_2_d9f504ad:

    # S "When she was stabbing his face over and over again..."
    S "Cuando le apuñalaba la cara una y otra vez..."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:254
translate spanish s_convi_2_11bc1507:

    # S "...she asked me how it is when you are in combat."
    S "... me preguntó qué se siente al estar en combate."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:255
translate spanish s_convi_2_429b6def:

    # S "And whether or not I..."
    S "Y si yo..."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:256
translate spanish s_convi_2_b5ea3532:

    # S "...liked the thrill of it."
    S "... disfrutaba de la adrenalina."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:259
translate spanish s_convi_2_d9c4f2e5:

    # S "...promise you don't judge me, okay?"
    S "... promete no juzgarme, ¿vale?"

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:262
translate spanish s_convi_2_ddb8bb74:

    # Z "Promise."
    Z "Te lo prometo."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:265
translate spanish s_convi_2_c33e3042:

    # S "We... somehow... started making out."
    S "Nosotras... no sé cómo... empezamos a enrollarnos."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:266
translate spanish s_convi_2_91a5fa7a:

    # S "I don't know why, but something in that situation just... drew me to her."
    S "No sé por qué, pero hubo algo en aquella situación que... me atrajo hacia ella."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:269
translate spanish s_convi_2_e4a837ff:

    # Z "[Q] is a pretty woman; I don't think less of you for it."
    Z "[Q] es una mujer muy guapa; no pienso menos de ti por ello."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:270
translate spanish s_convi_2_2e6ac8f0:

    # Z "I can tell you that whenever I come home after a fight, the excitement takes a while to subside. Your [persistent.mom] knows this well."
    Z "Te diré una cosa: cada vez que vuelvo a casa después de una pelea, la excitación tarda en bajar. Tu [persistent.mom] lo sabe bien."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:271
translate spanish s_convi_2_00e453d0:

    # Z "Violence makes the blood boil, and excitement takes many forms and finds many releases."
    Z "La violencia hace hervir la sangre, y la excitación puede adoptar muchas formas y buscar distintas maneras de salir."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:272
translate spanish s_convi_2_971a98df_1:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:273
translate spanish s_convi_2_b6fcaa73:

    # Z "These things happen. There is no shame in them."
    Z "Estas cosas pasan. No tienes por qué avergonzarte."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:276
translate spanish s_convi_2_2d9fb542:

    # S "I wonder if she genuinely likes me, or if that was just an act of hers."
    S "Me pregunto si le gusto de verdad o si todo fue una actuación por su parte."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:279
translate spanish s_convi_2_bceda1e9:

    # Z "I imagine she is a lonely woman on top of that pyramid."
    Z "Me imagino que es una mujer solitaria en la cima de esa pirámide."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:280
translate spanish s_convi_2_e7415417:

    # Z "Maybe she sees a potential friend in you?"
    Z "Quizá vea en ti a una posible amiga."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:283
translate spanish s_convi_2_539d0b24:

    # S "Maybe... I guess I will find out."
    S "Puede ser... Supongo que lo descubriré."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:290
translate spanish s_convi_2_18d04f4c:

    # S "But even if he threatened [A]..."
    S "Pero aunque amenazara a [A]..."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:293
translate spanish s_convi_2_b1c810c9_1:

    # S "I love her, and I would always protect her."
    S "La quiero, y siempre la protegería."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:296
translate spanish s_convi_2_f1d25812:

    # S "But torturing him like that..."
    S "Pero torturarle así..."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:297
translate spanish s_convi_2_456be2c7:

    # S "That's not right, you know?"
    S "Eso no está bien, ¿sabes?"

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:300
translate spanish s_convi_2_b12413c1_1:

    # Z "Our old Queen, the one who ruled before Merneith, would have agreed with you."
    Z "Nuestra antigua Reina, la que gobernaba antes de Merneith, habría estado de acuerdo contigo."

# game/scripts/convis_shani.rpy:305
translate spanish s_convi_2_6b1abe07:

